Description
-----------

Causes only the back face of a polygon with this material applied to render.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    backSided

Parameters
----------

Not Available.

Notes
-----

This keyword also activates the [noShadows](NoShadows_%28Material_global_keyword%29 "NoShadows (Material global keyword)") automatically.

